HOW THE SOFTWARE WORKS

The connectors interact with airline websites through your AI agent, on your
behalf, when you choose to run them. Each connector automates the process of
searching a specific airline's public-facing website or API — the same way a
human would search for flights in a browser. The Software does not access any
private, restricted, or authenticated airline systems beyond what is publicly
available to any user.
